{"tid":1463810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成日話港女崇洋，點知自己仲崇得勁過港女","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:57:02.000Z","uid":5649,"like":105,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd204311d2e741e979c7fb1c84f15a5315744de","tid":1463810,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"成個運動都兩個月，班白人食花生睇戲<br />\n實質咩都無幫到手<br />\n而家搞到佢地少少，佢地就即刻衝出黎維護自己權益<br />\n但連登仔仲覺得外國勢力好重要，佢地毛都唔比一條我地，我地反而要主動道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦連登仔，歐美無諗過幫我地手<br />\n佢地支持我地搞內亂傷害中共經濟咋<br />\n而家燒到佢地門口，阻到佢地國民一日半日就露出真面目<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己香港自己救啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"a833ca28be40d7999a4092df11b0d6b2f7797651","tid":1463810,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0eb0862c4c2a0a247d7464c9945fd8c08c8b63","tid":1463810,"uid":5649,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"簽能左幾百個聯署，班白人要幫手就一早幫左手啦"},{"pid":"656caf3a26d825c9423176657796bfa714f8ee58","tid":1463810,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f0432039bae7c9e502cc9a01a14c036693224b","tid":1463810,"uid":199590,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"成日ff美軍會嚟香港幫手打鳩g那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f50e063c3fcfc742956fd7e84a04feffe16037","tid":1463810,"uid":64464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":